From 3fdf28b5ce87bcaab7a80d34615a66272027f188 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 20:31:01 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/5] launcher: switch pad_launcher as entry for
 hybris_generic, restore system splash + faster startup

- feature/settings/build-profile.json5: entryModules -> ["pad_launcher"]
so
  Launcher.hap ships the pad module instead of phone, giving a
tablet-appropriate
  layout for the Volla Tablet (1600x2560).
- product/pad/EntryView.ets: fire bootevent.launcher.ready in onPageShow
(pad
  was the only EntryView without it, so bootanimation never got the
ready vote
  and hung on first boot). Drop RemoteWindowWrapper + its scale-to-0.95
handlers:
  windowAnimationManager.setController overrode the system
app-transition and
  suppressed startWindowIcon splashes. Falling back to the default
transition
  restores splashes and speeds up app open/close.
- product/pad/MainAbility.ts: create the desktop window before awaiting
RDB
  init so the first frame isn't gated on storage setup. Switch to
windowEvent +
  WindowEventType.WINDOW_ACTIVE (matches phone) and call
  launcherAbilityManager.checkBundleMonitor() on focus so bundle changes
  refresh. Stop destroying APP_CENTER_WINDOW on every onRequest.

Signed-off-by: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Change-Id: Ibe8572cc8f5b1b3672b28eb1864c1a390f5b114d
